- Copy config_dist.php to config.php and edit parameters
- If you don't have a FOAF profile, you can create one here: http://www.ldodds.com/foaf/foaf-a-matic
- Set the list of SMOB server you want to be able to push data to
- Chmod 777 the data directory
- Put those files in a webserver directory that can be accessed by any SMOB server you want to publish your data to
- You can add a .htaccess rule if you want to protect the publish interface
- That's all
